// "You have no maximum hand size." plus "{T}: Add {C}". The cap removal is a
// continuous player static ([CR#402.2] — the maximum hand size, normally seven,
// is removed entirely): `NoMax(HandSizeLimit)` is a dedicated op, not a value.
Normal(
  name: "Reliquary Tower",
  types: [
    Land,
  ],
  abilities: [
    Static(effects: [ModifyPlayer(You, NoMax(HandSizeLimit))]),
    Activated(cost: [Tap], effect: AddMana(1, Colorless)),
  ],
)
